'''Mayonnaise''' is an [[Artisan Goods|Artisan Good]] made using the [[Mayonnaise Machine]], taking 3 hours. 

[[Egg|Normal sized White and Brown eggs]] produce regular quality Mayonnaise. [[Large Egg|Large White and Brown eggs]] produce gold quality Mayonnaise. The quality of the egg is not a factor in determining the quality of the Mayonnaise.

[[Ostrich Egg|Ostrich Eggs]] produce 10 jars of Mayonnaise at once. Unlike chicken eggs, Ostrich Eggs produce Mayonnaise in the same quality as the egg. This is the only way to obtain a silver quality or iridium quality Mayonnaise.

[[Golden Egg|Golden Eggs]] produce 3 jars of Mayonnaise at gold quality at once, regardless of the quality of the eggs used.

