==Tailoring==
Mayonnaise is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a {{name|Shirt005|link=Tailoring{{!}}Light Blue Shirt|class=inline}}. It is a white dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed.

==Quests==
One Mayonnaise may be requested by [[Blobfish]], [[Catfish]], or [[Spook Fish]] in [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quests]].

